56:20.631 --> 56:23.232
<i>If I'm not feeling any less sour</i>

56:23.332 --> 56:28.873
<i>I promised myself to treat myself
and visit a nearby tower</i>

56:28.973 --> 56:31.605
<i>And climbing to the top</i>

